                 accuracy. We develop and validate correction methods that substantially reduce
                 these distortions, improving quantitative imaging of bone metastases.},
  html        = {https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-022-08847-0},
  doi         = {10.1038/s41598-022-08847-0},
}

